<TEXT>
madonna mae morgan didnt make much of an 
impact on this small northwest kansas town during her life but she 
has been the main topic of discussion since her death in march 
mrs morgans will left the city an estimated 1 million but 
the gift came with strings attached the town of about 2300 must 
raise a matching amount within two years and use the money to build 
a community center 
mrs morgan 88 was not wellknown in the town and the bequest 
caught nearly everyone by surprise 
we were absolutely stunned at first said city administrator 
jerry fear but everybody decided it was just too much money to 
pass up not many communities have this type of opportunity 
