change my way of thinking said roger handley a former ku klux 
klan leader in birmingham who was accused of attacking an sclc 
march in decatur in 1979 
the rev joseph lowery who organized the march is to lead the 
course saturday for the klansmen as part of a court settlement 
growing out of the bloody clash 
