concerned that unita might try to stage guerrilla attacks during 
mandelas stay 
increased rebel sabotage and bomb attacks this year have left 
luandans nervous and dependent on emergency electricity and water 
supplies 
mandelas arrival in angola came one day after de klerk started 
a ninenation european tour to gain international support for his 
attempts to reform south africa 
de klerk ordered mandelas release from prison and legalized the 
anc in february 30 years after the organization was banned 
